<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>구미 날씨 — 2026년 5월 4일</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #f4f4f0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    .header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .location { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .date { font-size: 13px; color: #888; margin-top: 2px; }
    .temps {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .temp-box {
      background: #f7f7f4;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .temp-label { font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .temp-value { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 600; }
    .temp-value.high { color: #BA7517; }
    .temp-value.low  { color: #378ADD; }
    .temp-value.diff { color: #444; }
    .timeline {
      background: #f7f7f4;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .timeline-title { font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .timeline-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .slot-label { font-size: 11px; color: #bbb; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .slot-icon { font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .slot-text { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; color: #333; }
    .alert {
      background: #EBF4FD;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #185FA5;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .source { font-size: 11px; color: #ccc; margin-top: 1.25rem; text-align: right; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <div>
        <div class="location">📍 구미, 경상북도</div>
        <div class="date">2026년 5월 4일 (월) — 내일 날씨 예보</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="temps">
      <div class="temp-box">
        <div class="temp-label">최고 기온</div>
        <div class="temp-value high">21°C</div>
      </div>
      <div class="temp-box">
        <div class="temp-label">최저 기온</div>
        <div class="temp-value low">9°C</div>
      </div>
      <div class="temp-box">
        <div class="temp-label">일교차</div>
        <div class="temp-value diff">12°C</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-title">시간대별 예보</div>
      <div class="timeline-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="slot-label">새벽</div>
          <div class="slot-icon">🌧️</div>
          <div class="slot-text">비</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="slot-label">오전</div>
          <div class="slot-icon">☁️</div>
          <div class="slot-text">흐림</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="slot-label">낮</div>
          <div class="slot-icon">☀️</div>
          <div class="slot-text">맑음</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="slot-label">저녁</div>
          <div class="slot-icon">🌤️</div>
          <div class="slot-text">구름 조금</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert">
      ℹ️ 일교차 12°C로 큼 — 겉옷 필수. 오전 외출 시 우산을 챙기세요.
    </div>

    <div class="source">출처: korea247.kr · 기상청 날씨누리</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
